#: ../../source/basic/installation.rst:7 04ea9ef1c1484206bd5b36de06d3f909
msgid ""
"Grammers-Python is a Python library, which means you need to download and"
" install Python from https://www.python.org/downloads/ if you haven't "
"already. Once you have Python installed, `upgrade pip <https://pythonspeed.com/articles/upgrade-pip/>`_ and run:"
msgstr ""
"grammers-python 是一个 Python  库，这意味着你需要先安装 Python。"
"你可以在 https://www.python.org/downloads/ 下载 Python。"
"安装好后运行以下命令来 `更新pip <https://pythonspeed.com/articles/upgrade-pip/>`_："

#: ../../source/basic/installation.rst:16 1c212a7dd43e4c5f9634a68565768921
msgid "…to install or upgrade the library to the latest version."
msgstr "...以及安装或更新本库"

#: ../../source/basic/installation.rst:21 f8c5f1b8f2f046c98d97caa6688e030f
msgid "Installing Development Versions"
msgstr "安装正在开发的版本"

#: ../../source/basic/installation.rst:23 003be7814e1644e89f3b32cba22eff37
msgid ""
"If you want the *latest* unreleased changes, you can run the following "
"command instead:"
msgstr ""
"如果你想体验未发布的最新功能，你可以运行下面的命令:"

#: ../../source/basic/installation.rst:32 31c56380a0d941ef86f7ef49e69ff619
msgid ""
"The development version may have bugs and is not recommended for "
"production use. However, when you are `reporting a library bug <https://github.com/HBcao233/grammers-python/issues/>`_, you "
